Title: Don't Prattle about God!
SeeAlso:
  - Title: Tao Te Ching
    Locus:
      Chapter: 56
---
It would be best if I stopped chattering
and kept silent about You, because when

I speak I say what I do not know, for I
cannot say what is true about You

who are beyond understanding --
but not beyond me.
